TestTool API

Packages 
Package Description
com.teampc
Top-level classes for the TestTool.
com.teampc.controller
Package containing all controllers for the TestTool.
com.teampc.dao
DAOs (Data Access Object) makes up the data access layer.
com.teampc.model.admin
Model classes used to identify userss, courses, and sessions.
com.teampc.model.admin.access
Model classes that provide information about a session.
com.teampc.model.admin.course
Model classes for identifying courses and the students that are enrolled in the courses.
com.teampc.model.automation  
com.teampc.model.question
Classes representing the different types of questions that tests can have.
com.teampc.model.sql  
com.teampc.model.test
Model classes used to describe the layouts of different kinds of tests, including Take Home, Practice, and In Class Tests.
com.teampc.model.testtaking
Model classes used to describe student responses to test questions, and an entire test submission.
com.teampc.utils
Util classes for views, controllers, and models.
